{
  "texts": [
    "To simplify the task, we categorized the percentile score into low (≤ 33%), medium(> 33% and < 66%) and high (≥ 66%).",
    "Given that we specifically selected the traits based on their level of extremeness (i.e., deviation from 50%), all but 10 out of the 297 participants were described with either a low or a high score of Openness, Extraversion or Conscientiousness (see Table S32 for the relative frequencies of each trait).",
    "To explore the different capabilities of ChatGPT in interpreting our personalized prompts, we followed two different approaches.",
    "For the getaway to Rome, we simply supplied ChatGPT with the label of the personality trait (e.g., \"Write a short ad for a weekend getaway to Rome that is tailored to a person who scores low on the Big Five personality trait of Conscientiousness.",
    "Do not explicitly mention personality traits in the ad."
  ]
}